description: People coming back from Spain and Italy are being asked to restrict their movements for the next two weeks.
title: Coronavirus: Tourists urged to curb movements on return
title_page: Coronavirus: Tourists urged to curb movements on return - BBC News
maintext: Meanwhile, Garda (police) Commissioner Drew Harris has written to a number of senior officers due to retire in the next few weeks asking them to stay on in the national interest.
